            <title>全新 Toyota Camry HEV 搭载第五代混能系统登场，以动力美学作设计核心</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/toyota-camry-hev-gen5/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=toyota-camry-hev-gen5</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/toyota-camry-hev-gen5/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 03:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[camry]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Lexus]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Toyota]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294277</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Toyota 自 1982 年推出 Camry 车系以来，全球累计销量突破 2,100 万辆，稳坐品牌最畅销车款之一的殊荣。2025 年皇冠汽车正式宣布推出搭载 Toyota 最新第五代混能系统的全新 Camry HEV，隆重登陆香港市场。新车不仅延续 Camry 的经典传承，更通过四大革新——外观设计、动力系统、智能配置与安全科技，为驾驶者带来升级体验。</span></p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294293" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_151642-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_151642-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_151642-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">全新 Camry HEV 以「动力美学」为设计核心，车身线条更流线动感，搭载全新「Hammerhead」C 字型 LED 头灯与低重心车头设计，搭配炙热红、瑰丽铜、深海蓝三款全新车色及 18 寸双色轮圈，时尚与实用兼备。动力方面，第五代混能系统结合 2.5L 引擎与电动马达，总输出达 230 匹马力，0 至 100 公里加速仅需 7.2 秒，油耗低至 19.6 km/L，较前代汽油版提升 38% 燃油效率，实现性能与节能的更佳平衡。</span></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294291" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152629-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152629-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152629-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152912-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152912-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152912-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">车厢内部同样重新设计，配备电子影像倒后镜、抬头显示器、前排冷暖通风座椅，以及后排首次加入的中央手枕控制面板，让乘客可自行调节座椅与冷气。三区域恒温冷气系统与 Nanoe X 空气净化功能进一步提升舒适度。安全配置上，新车标配 10 个气囊及 Toyota Safety Sense 3.0 主动安全系统，新增防护驾驶辅助功能，能提前侦测障碍物并提供转向与制动支援，确保行车安全。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_1528180-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_1528180-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_1528180-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152754-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152754-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152754-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">娱乐体验亦全面升级，12.3 寸触控屏幕支援无线 Apple CarPlay，搭配 JBL 9 喇叭音响系统，为车厢增添惬意氛围。全新 Camry HEV 售价由 HK$395,700 起（原价 HK$414,300），即日起于九龙湾、湾仔及沙田陈列室接受预订。</span></p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294292" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152258-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152258-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250226_152258-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />
规格:</h3><p><b>引擎型号: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">A25A-FXS</span></p><p><b>引擎类型: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">2.5L 直列四缸 VVT-iE D-4S 直喷引擎</span></p><p><b>引擎马力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">138 kW (187 PS) / 6,000 rpm</span></p><p><b>引擎扭力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">221 Nm / 3,200-5,200 rpm</span></p><p><b>电动马达类型: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">恒久磁石同步电动马达</span></p><p><b>电动马达马力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">100 kW (135 PS)</span></p><p><b>电动马达扭力: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">208 Nm</span></p><p><b>总混能系统输出: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">169 kW (230 PS)</span></p><p><b>油耗: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">19.6 km/L</span></p><p><b>0-100 km/h 加速: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">7.2 秒</span></p><p><b>车身尺寸: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">4,920 x 1,840 x 1,455 mm</span></p><p><b>轴距: </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">2,825 mm</span></p><p><strong>售价</strong>: <span style="font-weight: 400;">HK$395,700 起</span></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
